{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_Spectre3Attack}}
'''A_Spectre3Attack'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|SpectralLightningV2}} with the calling actor as its target, the calling actor's target as its tracer, a health of -2 and a vertical velocity of -12, then shoots twenty {{Class|SpectralLightningBall2}} in a 180° arc.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|SpectralMonster}} and derived classes.

